Method Returns Description <code>wa.on(event, h)</code> <code>() =&gt; void</code> Registers a listener. Call the returned function to detach it. <code>wa.once(event, h)</code> <code>() =&gt; void</code> Registers a one-shot listener. Returned function detaches it early. <code>wa.off(event, h)</code> <code>this</code> Removes a previously registered listener. Subscribe and unsubscribe<pre><code>const off = wa.on('message:created', (msg, chat) =&gt; {
